structure.unit: ARTICLE LIV. MIAMI-DADE COUNTY PRIVATE AMBULANCE SERVICE STUDY COMMITTEE

text.section:
Sec. 2-625. Reports.
The committee shall present quarterly progress report to the Public Safety and Community Services Committee and a written report thereon to the Board of County Commissioners, no later than March 1, 1994. The Commission shall review the final report of the committee and the ordinance. Upon submission of its report, the committee shall be dissolved.
